<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Ajustes | <%= displayTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #050505; --card: #0f0f0f; --blue: #007bff; --red: #dc3545; }
        body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: white; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        .header-server { padding: 20px 40px; background: var(--card); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        .container { padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; }
        .card { background: var(--card); padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #222; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #333; color: white; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn { padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 15px; }
        .btn-blue { background: var(--blue); color: white; }
        .btn-red { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--red); color: var(--red); }
        .btn-red:hover { background: var(--red); color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-server">
        <h1><%= server.name %></h1>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:10px;">
            <a href="/server/<%= server.id %>" style="color:gray; text-decoration:none;">Console</a>
            <a href="/server/<%= server.id %>/settings" style="color:white; text-decoration:none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue);">Settings</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h3 style="margin:0;">Información General</h3>
            <label style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;">Nombre del Servidor</label>
            <input type="text" value="<%= server.name %>">
            <button class="btn btn-blue">GUARDAR NOMBRE</button>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="border-color: var(--red);">
            <h3 style="margin:0; color: var(--red);">Zona de Peligro</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: gray;">Reinstalar el servidor borrará todos los archivos actuales y ejecutará el script de inicio de nuevo.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-red">REINSTALAR SERVIDOR</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>